body:
Hello, fellow Avicus forum user! 
This is a montage I made that shows some of the best moments I've gotten in the past few days in Nebula. It took me a lot of time and effort, so I would really love if you went and checked it out. The best parts are usually at the drops, in case you were wondering why the intro wasn't the greatest. Also, sorry for the 9-second blank-screen at the beginning of the video. I made a mistake with by clips and that accidentally happened.. I'll try to be more cautious about those in the future. Without farther ado, here it is! 
http://youtu.be/79r31lo_hWE
